smart-retail-platform/
 ├── config-service        # Spring Cloud Config
 ├── gateway-service       # API Gateway
 ├── product-service       # CRUD products
 ├── order-service         # Order placement
 ├── inventory-service     # Stock updates
 ├── analytics-service     # MongoDB logs + RxJava
 ├── legacy-service        # JDBC direct SQL
 └── frontend-dashboard    # Node.js + React
